# Supabase (Auth + Postgres) — provisioned via the Vercel Marketplace
# (`npx vercel integration add supabase`), not entered manually.
# Run `vercel env pull --environment=preview` to fetch real values locally.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# Also provisioned by the integration but not yet used by this app:
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET, POSTGRES_* (direct
# connection strings). Only add usage here if a feature actually needs
# server-side elevated access — don't wire these up speculatively.

# Discord bot — used server-side only (app/auth/callback/route.js) to
# auto-add a visitor to the Discord server on sign-in, via the
# `guilds.join` OAuth scope requested in app/enter/page.js. Set these
# yourself with `vercel env add` (do not paste the bot token in chat —
# it's a real secret, unlike the Supabase anon key above).
# Get the token: Discord Developer Portal -> your app -> Bot tab.
# Get the guild ID: enable Developer Mode in Discord, right-click your
# server icon -> Copy Server ID.
DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=
DISCORD_GUILD_ID=
